Teltoli / Kit
-----
Teltoli shakes her head a little, trying to clear the mech-fluid out of it. She had to stay conscious, so she could fight some more. Suddenly she sighed..

Who was she kidding? She wasn't a warrior! She had never fought before in her life! Apart from when she fought with her sister, but that was arguements! She couldn't fight to save her skin! 

Severely irratated with herself, Teltoli growls. But she does manage to calm herself down and walk over to Ramhorn, holding her stomch with one hand.

"Thank you.. for saving me"

-------

Kit goes to the explosion site and finds nothing, just a whole heap of blackened stuff. She sighs loudly and turns around, hearing another sound coming from a bush. It was that bot she had tried to fight.. the brother of Sinester. 

She grins and stalks stealithy over the area..
